ActStandards Council of Canada Act
PrecisAppointment of BRENT ALLAN SCHACTER of Winnipeg, Manitoba, to be a member of the Standards Council of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Glenn D. Feltham, whose term has expired.
